<p>Asks to borrow <hi rend="italic">Botanische Zeitung</hi> (1860) with Friedrich Alefeld on <hi rend="italic">Pisum</hi> [pp. 204–5].</p> 
            <p>JDH should ask George Busk whether he knows a better doctor than William Jenner "for giving life to a worn out poor devil".</p>
